_text = "When I look up into the sky, I look at the clouds. The clouds have always been there. They gaze down at me in every moment i've shared with these friends. The clouds have been there for all my camping trips, bike rides, and drives around Kelowna.\n\nI can’t help but let the clouds take me away from these memories. I take retreat in them, hiding rather than addressing these emotions face on.\n\nMy memory of them ends here."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom5, MemoryTunnelRoom5, false)
